{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/swiftui-text-number-of-lines/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<ul>\n<li>SwiftUI <code class=\"language-text\">Text</code>의 최대 라인 수를 강제해야할 때가 있다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Text</code>의 <code class=\"language-text\">.lineLimit(_:)</code> 함수를 사용하면 된다.</li>\n<li>아래 같이 최대 2줄까지만 보이는 <code class=\"language-text\">Text</code>를 만들어본다.\n<ul>\n<li>2줄보다 적은 양의 문구라면 모든 문구가 보이고, 2줄을 넘어가면 2줄까지만 보이고 마지막은 <code class=\"language-text\">...</code> 으로 짤린다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"articleImage\" style=\"border-radius: 19px; overflow: hidden;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1602px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/741a0932b6e90c1513bc918e441a0ca3/b5600/exampleText.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 86.14232209737828%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"exampleText\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/741a0932b6e90c1513bc918e441a0ca3/b5600/exampleText.png\" srcset=\"/static/741a0932b6e90c1513bc918e441a0ca3/b5600/exampleText.png 1602w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1602px) 100vw, 1602px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-swift line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ContentView</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">View</span>